Document: ButtonGroup  
Path: godot/classes/class_buttongroup.rst  
Summary: Methods for retrieving buttons and the currently pressed button in a group.  

Methods:  
- get_buttons() → Array<BaseButton>: Returns the list of buttons in the group.  
- get_pressed_button() → BaseButton: Returns the currently pressed button in the group.
