Document: ButtonGroup
Path: godot/classes/class_buttongroup.rst
Summary: Configures whether all buttons in the group can be unpressed simultaneously

Property: allow_unpress (bool) = false
Controls if all buttons in the group can be unpressed at once. When true, users can deselect all buttons simultaneously.

Methods:
- set_allow_unpress(value: bool)
- is_allow_unpress() → bool

Note: If true, it is possible to unpress all buttons in this ButtonGroup.
---CHUNK---
Document: ButtonGroup
Path: godot/classes/class_buttongroup.rst
Summary: Methods for retrieving buttons and pressed state in a ButtonGroup

Array of BaseButton get_buttons()  
Returns an Array of Button s who have this as their ButtonGroup (see BaseButton.button_group).

BaseButton get_pressed_button()  
Returns the current pressed button.